There is a pad under each table leg. The feet can protect your floor from being scratched. Multifunctional Side Table : Ample storage space is enough for you to store your family photos, lamp, books, alarm clock, TV remote etc, provide large storage space in your bedroom living room, all-purpose nightstand can meet your various storage needs in your bedroom. The deep oak wood tone combined retro and modern, it can be suitable for various styles of home decoration, adding a touch of unadorned elegance to your space.

Save Time : Measurements 15.4" D x 23.6" W x 22.1" H, With a clear instruction and numbered components, this charging nightstand will be finished quickly. Before installing this charging table, please check whether the accessories in the package are complete, if some accessories are missing, please contact us first, an accessory kit will be sent at free.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 13, 2024
reviews.reviewText: These were pretty easy to assemble and seem durable so far. The drawers seem to open smoothly, and provide a lot of space. The charging ports are a great addition. Love the darker color, matches my bedroom perfect!

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 22, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Amazing low profile nightstands
reviews.reviewText: I had seen a few reviews saying they weren’t sturdy. Which made me hesitant but I’m glad I still made the move and got them. I built the 2 nightstands within 2 hours..or within the Blues Brothers movie. Super simple instructions and they gave excess of every screw which was nice. They are very sturdy, don’t wobble at all and way nicer than the 14 yr old ikea nightstands we had. The plugs have a usb and usb-c slot which is convenient. I’m just really happy. The color is beautiful and it feels like it isn’t cheap like it won’t scratch very easy. And it all came packaged with styrofoam and styrofoam paper between every piece. We have a low profile platform bed so these low and wide nightstands were everything we were looking for. Honestly they seem as nice as furniture like an Ashley

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on December 18, 2023
reviews.reviewText: I'm updating my review as I've received outstanding customer service from Eva. She reached out immediately after I posted my review and offered a great solution that worked for both of us. We were excited about these end tables as they looked awesome on the Amazon site. They were not easy to put together and I'm disappointed with the overall sturdiness. As I said in the headline - it's just okay. It looks nice, but every time I pull the drawer out I'm waiting for it to break. My wife and I put furniture together a lot and I'm pretty sure it wasn't user error. All in all a decent product but not sure I'd recommend.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on February 7, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Sturdy and looks great
reviews.reviewText: These nightstands were super easy to put together. They don’t feel or look cheapy. love that it has the outlets on top. Def recommend!

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on September 15, 2023
reviews.reviewText: The media could not be loaded. I love the soft brown wood tone/color on these nightstands. It matches the vibe of my bedroom so well! I’m not usually a big fan of rattan material in general but I don’t mind it on these too much because it lightens up the pieces a bit and ties in the other light oak furniture pieces in the room. I also love the built-in outlet feature - it’s perfect for phone chargers so you don’t have to move furniture to find the wall outlets. Assembly instructions were very straightforward and each nightstand took me about 20 minutes putting them together on my own. They seem very sturdy and decent quality, and I expect they’ll last me for years. The price is awesome for a set of 2! Would definitely recommend.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on November 6, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 3.0 out of 5 stars Cute but very small
reviews.reviewText: These nightstands are really cute, it took be about a hour to put one together by myself. I didn't like the copper colored hardware so I spray painted them black. The only thing I dislike about this is it is SO SHORT, it's like a baby nightstand. I should have looked at the specs, so that's my fault. If you have a bed that's low to the floor it may be okay but if you have a taller bed or a bed with a box spring these will be way too short.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 13, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Great Quality and Sturdy
reviews.reviewText: These nightstands are really pretty, they will match better if you have a light color bed (see my pictures for an idea of a dark color bed - I didn’t love it).Love the plugs, they are very convenient for phone chargers and lamps.Assemble will take a while, much better if you have a drill. Drawers slide pretty easily and the nightstands are very sturdy. They are not very tall, works well with a bed that doesn’t have a box spring.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on December 3, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 4.0 out of 5 stars Good for the price
reviews.reviewText: Took about an hour to assemble both. We did them at the same time. A little wobbly, but I think we can mess with it and fix it. These are definitely short, but we have a low profile bed. I would purchase them again. Just remember, you get what you pay for. Instructions were very easy to follow.
